msgid "Updates"
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:7 d8be8f4ce93741be82f61ae3e15fd56e
msgid ""
"NethSecurity allows two types of updates, both available from the "
"``Update`` section under the ``System`` menu:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:9 f39d20636f094e6abcca1afb4ac14a36
msgid "normal updates for bugfixes and security patches"
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:10 79ed889571f5447582d93c9ba60535e6
msgid "system upgrades to switch to a different version"
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:13 f2f3401a35844d46a70c01174cd96f57
msgid "Bug & security fixes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:15 dfb2d464cdcd44068278217599f43641
msgid "These updates are intended for minor updates and bugfixes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:17 59dd584962f54d928ad713e5bfacfbd0
msgid ""
"Typically they could be performed automatically, but at any time it is "
"possible to check for new updates available by clicking on "
":guilabel:`Check for Fixes` button. These updates do not require a "
"restart of NethSecurity, they are tied to a specific version and "
"distributed using packages."
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:20 b7f464e0c9ed4cfa83ae662efade09e3
msgid ""
"When using this method, the version of the image shown inside the "
"dashboard does not change, but the system is updated with the latest "
"fixes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:25 94d52721122e4bf3ab66e8165488efd8
msgid "System upgrades"
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:27 8205163916274a1a8fa5e19fa7c59467
msgid ""
"This types of upgrages involve the transition to a new version of the "
"firmware that introduces new features, improvements and wider hardware "
"support."
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:31 aa50ee226a10448d95adc223bf3162f8
msgid ""
"The upgrade will preserve all the configurations and settings, but it "
"will not preserve extra packages installed by the user."
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:33 b61f04fb5c454badb537c781a0f6a383
msgid ""
"This type of update will reboot the device (which will therefore not be "
"reachable for a few dozen seconds) and then completely rewrites the "
"firmware, preserving all the configurations. However it is recommended to"
" save a configuration backup before proceeding with the upgrade."
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:36 2c2c98a3336440a78ef31805933c5b83
msgid ""
"If a new version is available, the user interface will display an "
"information banner and a dedicated button :guilabel:`Update System` that "
"will allow you to perform the update."
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:38 856975fa3a8d401dbefdbffdf0d33af7
msgid ""
"Alternatively, it is always possible to manually upload a compatible "
"image using the :guilabel:`Update with image file` button and proceed "
"with the update."
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:41 42b5fe0d49e14d4f83f37852e91b89d8
msgid "Update from command line"
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:42 08532c9628fb4368961c5a6fa5dae4ec
