msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:48 323925cc9728489ebb98333aca94fbdc
msgid "The ``sysupgrade`` command flashes the new image file to the device."
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:53 7f83555517584e1283d950c857535ec4
msgid "Restore extra packages"
msgstr ""

#: ../../updates.rst:55 5c527bb6ab2744889ba5c92048135195
msgid ""
"During the upgrade, the system will be completely rewritten, so all the "
"extra packages installed by the user will be lost. Still, the list of "
"installed packages is saved in the configuration backup, so it is "
"possible to restore them after the upgrade."
msgstr ""

